-- Senator Graham Sees ‘Very Little Republican Support’ for Hagel
-- B y   K e v i n   C o s t e l l o e
-- 2012-12-30T14:28:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-30/senator-graham-sees-very-little-republican-support-for-hagel.html
Senator Lindsey Graham  said he sees
“very little Republican support” for a possible nomination of
former Republican Senator Chuck Hagel as secretary of defense.  Graham, a South Carolina Republican, was speaking in an
interview broadcast today on “Fox News Sunday.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
